title: Ep 2133 - School Management Refuses Tanvis Admission
shortDesc: Ganpat and his family come to a school for Tanvi’s admission. The school management clears it to Ganpat that they can not admit Tanvi to the school.

title: Ep 2134 - Bhide Plans To Teach A Lesson To School Management
shortDesc: Ganpat tells Jethalal and his neighbours that the school management has rejected Tanvi’s admission. Bhide and his neighbours plan to teach a lesson to the school management for rejecting Tanvi’s school admission.

title: Ep 2135 - Mission Admission
shortDesc: Bhide and Madhavi plan to go to a school in the guise of a wealthy couple. Sodhi hires a luxurious car for them. Bhide family goes to the school for sting operation.

title: Ep 2136 - Tanvi And Bhide Family Meet The School Principal
shortDesc: Tanvi and her fake parents meet the school principal for her admission. The school administration happily agrees to admit Tanvi to the school.

title: Ep 2137 - Principal Admits Tanvi To School
shortDesc: Bhide informs the school principal that he has not recorded their conversation in his mobile phone. The school administration agrees to admit Tanvi in the school.

title: Ep 2138 - Kachre Ki Samasya
shortDesc: Anjali comes to Jethalal’s house and gifts him a box of sweets. Daya tells Jethalal that sweeper Malti is not keeping well. Popatlal asks Bhide to appoint a new ‘sweeper’ for their society.

title: Ep 2139 - Champaklal Ki Pratigya
shortDesc: Popatlal asks Bhide to appoint a new ‘sweeper’ for Gokuldham society. Champaklal Gada vows to not return to his house until he finds out a way to clean his society.

title: Ep 2140 - Champaklal Goes Missing
shortDesc:
Jethalal learns that his father Champaklal has gone missing from his society. Jethalal and his neighbours plan to search Champaklal.

title: Ep 2142 - Jethalal Files Champaklals Missing Complaint
shortDesc: Jethalal comes to a police station and tells Chalu Pande that his father Champaklal has gone missing. Police arrests Atmaram Bhide and Popatlal for their alleged role in Champaklal’s missing case.

title: Ep 2144 - Dustbin Ka Kamaal
shortDesc: Jethalal and his neighbours bring their dustbins in front of their houses. Champaklal informs his neighbours that he is going to put their dustbins in a dumpster.

title: Ep 2145 - Champaklal Gifts Dustbins To His Neighbours
shortDesc: Tapu sena distributes three dustbins to each and  every family of Gokuldham society. Champaklal instructs his neighbours to segregate their waste into three categories.

title: Ep 2146 - Champaklal Turns Household Waste Into Compost
shortDesc: Champaklal informs his neighbours that their household waste has been composted. Champaklal’s neighbours congratulate him and Tapu sena for their innovative idea and hard work.

title: Ep 2147 - Tapus Friends Plan To Celebrate His Birthday
shortDesc: Tappu’s friends come to his house at midnight to wish him for his birthday. Jethalal stops them from meeting Tapu. He clears it to them that Tapu is having rest in his room.
